extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalMovieRental], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The movieRental has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Movies:] !{data.movie_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.movie_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.movie_instance_available_count}
      li #[strong Producers:] !{data.producer_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}
